♪ So now I wake up
every day ♪

41:10.048 --> 41:13.834
♪ And see her
standing there ♪

41:13.868 --> 41:17.404
♪ Just waiting
for a partner ♪

41:17.439 --> 41:21.308
♪ To compose ♪

41:21.342 --> 41:25.846
